# Copy Centralization Guidelines

## Current State (Needs Implementation)
Copy is currently hardcoded in components. Need to centralize.

## Planned Structure
```
app/copy/
  error-messages.ts    # All error messages
  help-text.ts         # All help text and tooltips
  ui-copy.ts           # All UI strings (tile names, labels, buttons)
  email-templates.ts   # All email content
  theme-hotrod.ts      # Hot Rod AN themed variants (optional)
```

## Error Messages Pattern (from [docs/design/error_message_localization_audit.md](mdc:docs/design/error_message_localization_audit.md))

```typescript
// app/copy/error-messages.ts
export enum ErrorCode {
  APPROVAL_FAILED = 'APPROVAL_FAILED',
  NETWORK_ERROR = 'NETWORK_ERROR',
  NOT_FOUND = 'NOT_FOUND',
  UNAUTHORIZED = 'UNAUTHORIZED',
}

export const ERROR_MESSAGES: Record<ErrorCode, string> = {
  [ErrorCode.APPROVAL_FAILED]: 'Approval couldn't be processed. Please try again.',
  [ErrorCode.NETWORK_ERROR]: 'Network error. Please check your connection.',
  [ErrorCode.NOT_FOUND]: 'The requested item could not be found.',
  [ErrorCode.UNAUTHORIZED]: 'You don't have permission to perform this action.',
};

// Future: ERROR_MESSAGES_FR, ERROR_MESSAGES_ES for i18n
```

## Help Text Pattern (from [docs/design/help_text_localization_audit.md](mdc:docs/design/help_text_localization_audit.md))

```typescript
// app/copy/help-text.ts
export const HELP_TEXT = {
  PICKER_PAYMENT: {
    TOTAL_PIECES: "Number of pieces in this order for picker payment calculation",
    PAYOUT_AMOUNT: "Calculated based on pieces: 1-4 = $2, 5-10 = $4, 11+ = $7",
  },
  ESCALATION: {
    NOTE_PLACEHOLDER: "Add context for audit trail",
  },
};
```

## Usage in Components
```tsx
import { HELP_TEXT } from "~/copy/help-text";

<TextField
  label="Total Pieces"
  helpText={HELP_TEXT.PICKER_PAYMENT.TOTAL_PIECES}
/>
```

## Benefits
- Single source of truth
- Easy to update copy
- Ready for i18n/translation
- Consistent messaging
- Better maintainability
